OL,3,CHow the war in Iran is turning crisis
OL,4,Cto disaster in Somalia
OL,6,FThe disruption caused by the war in
OL,7,Fthe Middle East is risking making a
OL,8,Fdire situation in Somalia even worse,
OL,9,Fwith fuel, food and fertiliser
OL,10,Fsupplies all heavily impacted by the
OL,11,Fclosure of the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,13,FAid agencies have been warning that
OL,14,Fthe disruption to the global economy
OL,15,Fwill have a severe impact on several
OL,16,Fimpoverished African nations, many of
OL,17,Fwhich rely heavily on exports from the
OL,18,FGulf region to keep their economies
OL,19,Fgoing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
