OL,3,CHow the war in Iran is turning crisis
OL,4,Cto disaster in Somalia
OL,6,FThe sharp rise in fuel prices has also
OL,7,Fled to delays and cancellations of
OL,8,Fvital food supplies to war-torn
OL,9,Fregions, severely impacting aid
OL,10,Fprogrammes in the region.
OL,12,FUNICEF says it has more than #10m
OL,13,Fworth of lifesaving supplies,
OL,14,Fincluding food, vaccines, and mosquito
OL,15,Fnets, in transit or being prepared for
OL,16,Fdelivery to Somalia, all of which is
OL,17,Fnow hanging in the balance due to the
OL,18,Fconflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
