OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774775625
OL,3,CHow the war in Iran is turning crisis
OL,4,Cto disaster in Somalia
OL,6,FWhile aid-reliant Somalia could be the
OL,7,Fworst impacted by the war, many other
OL,8,Fnations are also feeling the squeeze.
OL,10,FHow has the war impacted Somalia and
OL,11,Faid operations in the region?
OL,13,FCatherine Russell, UNICEF's executive
OL,14,Fdirector, said the Iran war has been a
OL,15,F"shock to the system" for the agency's
OL,16,Fwork on the ground in Somalia.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774775625
OL,3,CHow the war in Iran is turning crisis
OL,4,Cto disaster in Somalia
OL,6,F"It means that we can't get supplies
OL,7,Fin as easily, and that fuel costs are
OL,8,Freally high," she said. "It's another
OL,9,Fproblem that we have to try to deal
OL,10,Fwith, and it means that more and more
OL,11,Fchildren will suffer."
OL,13,FAt the same time, more than 400 health
OL,14,Fand nutrition facilities have closed
OL,15,Fover the past year across Somalia,
OL,16,Fmainly due to US funding cuts, leaving
OL,17,Fmany communities without access to
OL,18,Fsupport. Aid agencies warn more
OL,19,Fclosures could follow.
OL,26,@pD@MO]pD@YOUsD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
