OL,3,CHow the war in Iran is turning crisis
OL,4,Cto disaster in Somalia
OL,6,FIn Somalia's capital, Mogadishu, the
OL,7,Fgovernment warned last month that
OL,8,Fnearly 6.5 million people face severe
OL,9,Fhunger as the drought worsens and
OL,10,Fconflict, as well as global aid cuts,
OL,11,Fintensify the country's crisis.
OL,13,FThe latest data from a report by the
OL,14,FIntegrated Food Security Phase
OL,15,FClassification, a global hunger
OL,16,Fmonitoring group, estimates that 1.84
OL,17,Fmillion children under five in Somalia
OL,18,Fare expected to suffer acute
OL,19,Fmalnutrition in 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
