PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774775625
OL,3,CHow the war in Iran is turning crisis
OL,4,Cto disaster in Somalia
OL,6,FMany of these issues were present
OL,7,Fbefore the war, but the UN and several
OL,8,Faid organisations say it has made
OL,9,Fthings far worse.
OL,11,FUNICEF says the war is making food,
OL,12,Fmedicines, fuel and water more
OL,13,Fexpensive to move, while in drought-
OL,14,Faffected areas, water costs have more
OL,15,Fthan doubled because scarcity is
OL,16,Frising and fuel for deliveries is
OL,17,Fbecoming unaffordable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
