PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774775625
OL,3,CHow the war in Iran is turning crisis
OL,4,Cto disaster in Somalia
OL,6,FThe World Food Programme (WFP) has
OL,7,Fsaid surging food and fuel prices from
OL,8,Fthe escalation in the Middle East
OL,9,Fconflict are likely to worsen hunger
OL,10,Ffor vulnerable populations "in the
OL,11,Fregion and beyond," not just in the
OL,12,Fcountries directly at war.
OL,14,FThey said the blocking of the Strait
OL,15,Fof Hormuz has created a "dual
OL,16,Fchokepoint" for food supplies, with
OL,17,Fmuch of the world's natural gas used
OL,18,Fin fertiliser produced in the region,
OL,19,Fas well as blocking critical oil
OL,20,Fexports.
OL,26,@rD@\OUsD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
