OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774775625
OL,3,CHow the war in Iran is turning crisis
OL,4,Cto disaster in Somalia
OL,6,FWFP has also diverted shipping in the
OL,7,Fregion from the Suez Canal amid fears
OL,8,Fof being caught up in the conflict,
OL,9,Fforcing them to send supplies the much
OL,10,Flonger way around South Africa.
OL,12,FThe World Health Organization has also
OL,13,Fsaid its operations in the region have
OL,14,Fbeen disrupted by the conflict, with
OL,15,Fits Dubai Logistics Hub for Global
OL,16,FHealth Emergencies closed due to the
OL,17,Fstrikes against the United Arab
OL,18,FEmirates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774775625
OL,3,CHow the war in Iran is turning crisis
OL,4,Cto disaster in Somalia
OL,6,FThe Red Cross has reported similar
OL,7,Fissues, with the organisation
OL,8,Freporting costs for moving aid have
OL,9,Fgone up by 70% on average and by 300%
OL,10,Fon some routes. Similar problems have
OL,11,Falso been reported with land and air
OL,12,Ftransport.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FSomalia's citizens are also being
OL,20,Fimpacted, with the price of fuel
OL,21,Fhaving shot up because of the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
