OL,3,CHow the war in Iran is turning crisis
OL,4,Cto disaster in Somalia
OL,6,FReuters reported drivers of tuktuk
OL,7,Ftaxis in Somalia's capital are
OL,8,Fabandoning their livelihoods because
OL,9,Ffuel prices make their fares
OL,10,Funprofitable.
OL,12,FHow is the conflict impacting the rest
OL,13,Fof the continent?
OL,15,FWhile most other African nations are
OL,16,Fnot as heavily dependent on aid
OL,17,Fsupplies as Somalia, their economies
OL,18,Fhave been impacted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
