OL,3,CHow the war in Iran is turning crisis
OL,4,Cto disaster in Somalia
OL,6,FAfrica imports most of the petroleum
OL,7,Fproducts it consumes, with much of it
OL,8,Fcoming from the Middle East.
OL,10,FFuel shortages have been reported in
OL,11,FKenya, with several petrol stations
OL,12,Frunning out of supplies.
OL,14,FReuters also reported Mauritius is
OL,15,Fstruggling to keep fuel flowing after
OL,16,Fexpected deliveries were cancelled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
