OL,3,CHow the war in Iran is turning crisis
OL,4,Cto disaster in Somalia
OL,6,FThe fertiliser shortage is also having
OL,7,Fan impact, with early rains in East
OL,8,FAfrica leaving a small window for
OL,9,Fplanting crops, meaning the price
OL,10,Fhikes have come at the worst time.
OL,12,FEven tiny delays in planting can lead
OL,13,Fto a significant reduction in output
OL,14,Fwhen it comes to harvest.
